1.0 beta 8
----------
* Documentation of resouces.
* <delete> entry in sitemap.
* JAXP interface to XML parser and XSLT processor, 
  no dependency on Xerces or Xalan anymore (hopefully...).
* Prototyp integration with Apache Batik for SVG rendering.
* <part> entry in sitemap.


1.0 beta 9
----------
* Support for XML islands, primary for SVG.


1.0 beta 10
-----------
* General support for XML islands
* LSP extension elements and functions.
* Better documentation.


1.0 beta 11
-----------
* Support for non-reentrant FileStorages: XML islands works together with FTP.
* Documentation of the plugin API for FileStorages.
* Apache Ant task for Lagoon.


1.0 beta 12
-----------
* GUI for Lagoon.


1.0 beta 13
-----------
* Better GUI.


1.0 beta 14
-----------
* Updated support for Apache Batik 1.1.1.
* Updated support for Apache FOP 0.20.3.
* Updated LSP.
* Checks for broken FTP connection (timeout) and reconnect.
* Fixed display bug in GUI for Java2 1.4.


1.0 beta 15
-----------
* <output> entry in sitemap
* Better general support for XML islands, without using LSP.


1.0 beta 16
-----------
* Better handling of DTDs.
* Project properties in sitemap.
* LSP will let processing instructions through. Useful for PHP.
* <lsp:element> and <lsp:attribute>.


1.0 beta 17
-----------
* Now requires Java2 1.4 or later.
* Support for Java2 container classes.
* Made LSP independent from Lagoon.
* Standalone LSP compiler.
* Conditional if...then...else expression in LSP.


1.0 beta 18
-----------
* Compile LSP into Java bytecode for better performance.
* LSP Extension functions implemented as Java methods.


1.0 beta 19
-----------
* LSP available as separate package.
* LSSI.


1.0 beta 20
-----------
* Better Batik integration for SVG rendering: xlinks now works.

  
1.0 beta 21
-----------
* Fixed problem with updated stylesheet not triggering update of multiple 
  dependent files.

1.0 beta 22
-----------
* Can be compiled and used with both Java 1.4 and 
  Java 1.5 (also known as 5.0).
* XML formatter supports omit-xml-declaration.
